76561198026990891,Recommended,214360,33913579,Posted: 30 July,all,VulcanXtian,"I've played this game a lot and love this game personally. If you like competitive multiplayer tower defense, it's perfect. Very well done. Unit and tower variety, good ""talent tree"" system, gameplay is smoth and bug-free. Also family-friendly if that's important to you.My only complaints with the gameplay are the zoombots are a little too strong if you rush them early and the games aren't as fast-paced as I'd prefer, but no big deal. Also the tower system is a little strange, attacking shields first, then armor, then health. Since you have to build crossbow towers for first towers, that means mid-late game you must sell the weaker crossbow towers near entry to replace with the electric and canon towers first, then place your crossbow towers after that. Otherwise you won't deal damage effectively.*Note: The multiplayer is dead nowadays. Only good against the AI bot or if you have a friend to create a private 1v1 match with. My friend and I will still do some occasional 1v1 duels on this game. It's too bad because if they released new content and updates and kept the multiplayer alive, it could have been amazing."
